'''Likarion Wainaina''' (yavutse 20 Kanama 1987), ni [[Uburusiya|umuRussiya]]  uturuka [[Kenya]] ukina filimi . Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa filimi ngufi izwi cyane ''Between the Lines''  na ''Bait'' ndetse na filime ya [[Kenya]] yahawe ibihembo byinshi mu mateka, ''Supa Modo'' . <ref>https://www.trigon-film.org/en/directors/Likarion_Wainaina</ref> Usibye gukora firime, ni n'umukinnyi wa sinema, umwanditsi na  producer . <ref name="standardmedia">https://www.standardmedia.co.ke/entertainment/lifestyle/2001277821/i-am-a-high-school-dropout-meet-russian-born-auntie-boss-director-likarion-wainaina?amp=1 </ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 20 Kanama 1987 i Moscou, mu [[Burusiya]] ku babyeyi bava  [[Kenya]]. Igihe yari afite imyaka ine, yimukiye muri [[Kenya]] n'umuryango we. <ref name="yale">https://african.macmillan.yale.edu/likarion-wainaina</ref> Afite mushiki we na barumuna be babiri. <ref name="standardmedia">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.standardmedia.co.ke/entertainment/lifestyle/2001277821/i-am-a-high-school-dropout-meet-russian-born-auntie-boss-director-likarion-wainaina?amp=1 "I am a high school dropout: Meet Russian-born 'Auntie Boss' director"]. Standard Media<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">4 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye akora firime hanyuma yimukira mu ikinamico. Yabaye umunyamuryango wa theatre ya Phoenix Players i Nairobi kuva 2007<ref>https://nairobinow.wordpress.com/tag/likarion-wainaina/</ref>. Nyuma yaje gukora nk'umuyobozi w'ikinamico. Hagati aho, yanakoraga mu nganda za firime nka gaffer na cinematografi. Nkumukinnyi wa cinemateri yakoraga kuri documentaire nyinshi, kwamamaza no kuri televiziyo.  Muri 2013, yashinze isosiyete Kibanda Pictures<ref>https://african.macmillan.yale.edu/likarion-wainaina</ref>. 

Muri 2013, yakoze firime ngufi ''Between the Lines'' yaje kuba Filime ya mbere yo muri [[Kenya]] yerekanwe kuri ecran ya IMAX muri [[Kenya]]. Muri make yakiriwe neza hanyuma atorwa muri AMCVA awards 2015 igihembo cyiza cya Media Media Award<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/likarion-wainaina/</ref>. Hanyuma yayoboye filime ngufi ''Bait'' muri 2015, yatoranijwe mu iserukiramuco rya Filime Amasaha 48. Ifoto yatsindiye kandi ibihembo byinshi birimo Umuyobozi mwiza, ibihembo byabateze amatwi hamwe nigihembo cyabacamanza. Yatoranijwe kandi nka imwe muri firime ngufi zerekanwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2016.  Muri 2018, yakoze firime ngufi, ''My Faith'', yatsindiye Filime Nziza yo muri [[Afurika]] y'Iburasirazuba mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Mashariki. <ref>https://www.standardmedia.co.ke/entertainment/lifestyle/2001277821/i-am-a-high-school-dropout-meet-russian-born-auntie-boss-director</ref>

Muri 2018, yatangiye gukina filime ya ''Wavamizi'' . Hanyuma muri uwo mwaka, yerekanwe bwa mbere muri firime na ''Supa Modo'', yamamaye cyane. <ref>https://www.trigon-film.org/en/movies/Supa_Modo</ref> Filime yagaragaye bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya 68 rya Berlin. <ref>https://www.berlinale.de/en/presse/pressemitteilungen/alle/Alle-Detail_39636.html</ref> Nyuma yaje gutoranywa [[nkumunyakenya]] winjira muri Filime nziza yindimi zamahanga mu bihembo bya 91 bya Academy, ariko ntibyatoranijwe. <ref>https://www.kenyans.co.ke/news/33539-supa-modo-kenyas-submission-oscars-rafiki-loses-out</ref> <ref>https://variety.com/2018/film/news/supa-modo-kenya-berlinale-crowd-pleaser-oscar-hopeful-1202961174/</ref> Hamwe nibi bihembo byose, film ibaye firime yahawe ibihembo byinshi muri [[Kenya]] kandi ikunzwe nabanegura. <ref>https://www.screenafrica.com/2019/06/18/film/business/director-speak-likarion-wainaina/</ref>

Yakoraga kuri tereviziyo yamamaza amata ya Pascha na Santa Maria. Yayoboye Filime icyenda za Magic Magic Original Films (AMOF) hamwe na sitcom ya TV yitwa ''Classmates''. Muri 2016, yakoze filimi ''Auntie Boss!'' cyanyuze kuri NTV nyuma y'urupfu rw'umuyobozi wambere Derrick Omfwoko Aswani. <ref>https://kiss100.co.ke/actordirector-omfwoko-passes-on/</ref> Hagati aho, yari umukinnyi wa sinema amashusho yindirimbo za Sarabi Band yakoze 'Tumechoka' na 'Haujali' ndetse na cinematografi mumashusho yindirimbo 'Loneliness' yaririmbwe na Liron. 

